title: Suit settled over car used in 'Back to the Future' films
text: Suit settled over car used in 'Back to the Future' films Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (15 minutes ago) In time for "Back to the Future" day, the widow of the automaker whose famous car traveled through time in the 1985 movie and its sequels has settled a lawsuit over the use of his name.
